{
  "texts": [
    "The other three phases form the computational procedure that is required to generate top-N recommendations.",
    "The procedure phases of the proposed Fusion-based semantic collaborative filtering are demonstrated in detail as follows: Phase 1: Ontology Construction and Items Ratings ExtractionTo empower a recommendation system, ontology construction and item ratings extraction must be undertaken.",
    "Using the Protégé editor, ontology repository, a structured knowledge base encompassing related concepts, relationships, and attributes, are constructed.",
    "We acknowledge the inherent complexity involved in constructing ontologies, and its feasibility within this context relies on well-defined domain ontology.",
    "This includes the utilization of appropriate tools, understanding dataset characteristics, and aligning with the primary goal of enhancing the recommendation system."
  ]
}